snippet.title: Mazes of Karradash 2 - Character creation, equipment and city facilities
snippet.description:
"Mazes of Karradash 2" is a new dungeon crawl in development for iOS and Android.
You have 8 races and 10 classes to unlock in Karradash 2. Furthermore, you can choose from 8 different traits to customize your character.

http://www.68kstudios.com
https://www.facebook.com/68kstudios/
